Package <Unnamed>

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Car
    The Car class is a class which function is to initialize Car-type objects, and to mantain them in memory.
    CarsDB
    The CarDB class is a class which works with the car table of the mySQL DB.
    CarsPanel
    The CarsPanel class is a fundamental class of the application it shows the list of cars present in DB, and permits the user to delete or add cars.
    Frame
    The Frame class is a fundamental class of the application it simply initializes a frame with all the panels.
    Frame.about_click
    ActionListener which permits to everyone to get some specific information about the APP.
    Frame.close_click
    ActionListener which permits to everyone to close the APP.
    Frame.exit_click
    WindowListener which performs some actions when the close button is pressed.
    Frame.importer_click
    ActionListener which permits to each user to import new cars from a .txt or .dat file.
    Frame.logout_click
    ActionListener which permits to the user to logout.
    Log
    The Log class is a class used to mantain a cronology of errors inside 5 .dat files.
    LoginPanel
    The LoginPanel class is a fundamental class of the application it is used to log inside the application.
    MainPagePanel
    The MainPagePanel class is a class of the application which shows a Welcome message to the user.
    MainPanel
    The Main class is a fundamental class of the application it simply initializes the main panel of the application.
    MyInfoPanel
    The MyInfoPanel class is a fundamental class of the application it simply contains the infos about the user and permits to add an image.
    Seller
    The Seller class is a class which function is to initialize Seller-type objects, and to mantain them in memory.
    SellerDB
    The SellerDB class is a class which works with the user table of the mySQL DB.
    SellersPanel
    The SellersPanel class is a class which function is to show all the Sellers, and gives the possibility to delete users.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    BadlyClosedChooseException
    The BadlyClosedChooseException class is an extra exception class which is called when an JFileChooser is badly closed.
    DeleteAllException
    The DeleteAllException class is an extra exception class which is called when all the users or all the cars are being deleted.
    ExistingUserException
    The ExistingUserException class is an extra exception class which is called when a someone tries to create a new user with the same name of an existing one.
    LoginFailedException
    The LoginFailedException class is an extra exception class which is called when a login fails.
    WrongFormatException
    The WrongFormatException class is an extra exception class which is called when same invalid data is inserted or imported.
